---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy | Andrea Diotallevi Art"
    description="Learn how your personal data is collected, used, and protected. No accounts, simple checkout, optional newsletter, and basic analytics."
>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center px-4 py-8 pt-0 md:pt-8 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto text-gray-800"
    >
        <div class="w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-2/3">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="mb-6">
                I respect your privacy and keep things simple. I do <strong>not</strong> offer user
                accounts or sign-ins. I only collect the information needed to process your order,
                respond to enquiries, and, if you choose, send occasional updates.
            </p>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Who I am</h2>
                <p>
                    This website is operated by Andrea&nbsp;Diotallevi. For any privacy questions,
                    please use the <a class="text-blue-700 underline font-semibold" href="/contact">contact page</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Data I collect</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        <strong>Orders (via Stripe Checkout)</strong>: name, email, shipping address, order
                        details. Payment details are handled securely by Stripe and are <em>not</em> stored
                        on this site.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Contact form</strong>: name, email, and your message so I can reply.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Newsletter (optional)</strong>: your email address if you subscribe. You can
                        unsubscribe anytime via the link in emails.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Analytics and usage</strong>: basic site analytics (e.g. Google Analytics 4)
                        to understand page views and improve the site. This may use cookies or similar
                        technologies.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Local preferences</strong>: limited data like your locale or cart/session
                        information to make the shopping experience work smoothly.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">How I use your data</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>To process and deliver your orders and provide customer support.</li>
                    <li>To respond to messages you send via the contact page.</li>
                    <li>To send optional newsletter updates if youâ€™ve subscribed.</li>
                    <li>To maintain, secure, and improve the website.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Legal bases</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Contract</strong>: processing orders and customer service.</li>
                    <li><strong>Consent</strong>: sending newsletters; certain analytics/cookies where required.</li>
                    <li><strong>Legitimate interests</strong>: basic analytics, site security, and fraud prevention.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Sharing and processors</h2>
                <p class="mb-2">
                    I share data only with trusted service providers to run the site and fulfil orders:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Stripe</strong> for secure payments.</li>
                    <li><strong>Printing and fulfilment partners</strong> to produce and ship your order.</li>
                    <li><strong>Hosting and infrastructure</strong> providers to operate this website.</li>
                    <li><strong>Email services</strong> for order and contact communications, and newsletters if you opt in.</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics</strong> to understand site performance and improve content.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-2">
                    I do not sell your personal data.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">International transfers</h2>
                <p>
                    Some providers may process data outside your country. I rely on their safeguards
                    (such as standard contractual clauses) and industry-standard security to protect your data.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Retention</h2>
                <p>
                    Order records are kept for as long as necessary for accounting, tax, and legal
                    obligations. Contact messages and newsletter data are retained only as long as
                    needed to provide the service or until you ask me to delete them.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Your rights</h2>
                <p class="mb-2">
                    You may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict your personal data. To
                    exercise these rights, please use the <a class="text-blue-700 underline font-semibold" href="/contact">contact page</a>.
                </p>
                <p>
                    For newsletters, use the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any email.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Cookies</h2>
                <p>
                    This site uses essential cookies (for cart/session and preferences) and may use
                    analytics cookies (e.g. GA4) to measure traffic. You can adjust your browser settings
                    to manage cookies.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Questions about this policy or your data? Please <a class="text-blue-700 underline font-semibold" href="/contact">get in touch</a>.
                </p>
            </section>

            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-GB")}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

